Description:

Ramchand Pakistani (2008)

Director: Mehreen Jabbar
Writers: Mohammad Ahmad (screenplay), Javed Jabbar
Screenplay: Mohammad Ahmed
Music composed by: Debojyoti Mishra
Running time: 105 minutes

Cast:
Nandita Das
Rashid Farooqui
Maria Wasti
Nouman Ijaz
Syed Fazal Hussain

Storyline:
Ramchand Pakistani is a Pakistani Urdu film that tells a true story about a boy who inadvertently crosses the border between Pakistan and India and the following ordeal that his family has to go through. A 7 year old Pakistani boy and his father belonging to the untouchable Hindu caste accidentally cross the border and spend years in an Indian jail while the mother on the other side doesn't know what has happened to them.
